item.title: Speednet Internet broadband service direct results
item.description: What is Speednet Khulna? Speednet is a broadband internet service provider in Khulna city. Khulna situated on the Southeast side of Bangladesh. Bangladesh is a small country on the Southeast Asia border with India and Myanmar. Bangladesh has the world’s largest Sandy beach Cox’s Bazaar and the Largest mangrove forest Sundarban. Khulna is a port city name Mongla Port, is the second-largest port of Bangladesh after Chittagong port. Speednet internet supplier started the journey in Khulna city.
